r the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"2f7bb110987536ad49acf6e9127423b10839ab74","tid":2094791,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"deefe887d1c5fc15f372d53dd8612ff7c4e0a0ab","tid":2094791,"uid":50502,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"015ccb11a203517cc80ebb5297c5ad727897bbec","tid":2094791,"uid":215706,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"岩啊  呢班撚樣講一息尚存抗爭到底<br />\n講堅守公義寸步不讓<br />\n講撐手足撐到底  又乜又柒咁<br />\n<br />\n一個國安法埋黎  毛都未郁佢一條<br />\n全部又拆連儂牆又玩數字又底線又諧音乜乜咁<br />\n縮撚到分返2粒卵子精子分別入返老母個巢同老豆粒丸度咁<br />\nbno平權啊  正喎走先  手足我地都係唔煲底見啦<br />\n英國見啦 bye bye <br />\n<br />\n入左去果啲手足  出左事果啲手足<br />\n唔係condom 係乜野<br />\n<br />\n香港人  我真係笑而不語  再咁落去  直頭係恥與為伍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:45:26.000Z","msg":"已經唔係當唔當condom<br />\n而係抗爭目標 勝利既定義變左制裁香港 移民國外<br />\n堅持光復香港既手足：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hd0gr4C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhd0gr4C.jpg&h=6fc521c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"exactly  我都開始覺得為香港呢排人抗爭<br />\n手足真係on9左  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ebf34c43975c95835e7d5f0d21afcd5fbdbbcb"